x = tf.constant([4, 12, 8, 8])

new_x = tf.squeeze(tf.nn.conv1d(tf.reshape(x, [1, int(x.shape[0]), 1]), tf.ones([2, 1, 1], dtype=tf.int32), 1, 'VALID'))
